high_descs: Pick up the yellow knife from the table.
Exit the bedroom and turn left to walk to the kitchen sink.
Wash the knife in the sink and pick up the knife.
Turn left and walk to the diningtable.
Set the knife down on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed Knife on the DiningTable

high_descs: head toward the wall then turn left to reach the dressingtable.
Pick up the knife from the table.
exit the room and go straight turn right to reach the sink.
Put the knife into the sink and pour the water and clean it.
Take the cleaned knife and turn left to reach the diningtable.
Place the cleaned knife on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Take the cleaned Knife put on the round DiningTable.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the dressingtable.
Take the knife from the white table.
Turn around and leave the room, take left and take another left and walk towards the sink.
Put the knife in the sink and wash it and take the knife out from the sink.
Take left, walk straight and move to the diningtable.
Keep the knife in the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: To wash the Knife and keep it in the DiningTable.
